content: I never saw Shadow mentioned in regard to the captain sections. I told someone I knew nothing. For some reason I was put in a Tech room by myself to answer questions. Two hours there, maybe five minutes of actually seeing what to do. Captains: if someone says they know nothing,  assume they know nothing and tell them to label themself as Shadow something Captain. New people in Captain: rename yourself as Shadow ___ Captain if you know nothing. I was there for two hours before someone told me I should have labelled as Shadow.
Hi <@911700060360818688> -- Are you in the VOTE Team channels yet? Your feedback is very  important but I need to flag it there for the right people to see it.
<@1263159708466811000> -- Tagging you here so you can see quickly.
No. I don't see anything that says Vote Team.
Always label if you are a shadow... always.
Hi Bill, you're now in our VOTE Team channel. Where did you sign up to shadow? We had instructions on our sign up links to label shadow, my apologies again for the confusion!
